001package react4j.dom.proptypes.html;
002
003import javax.annotation.Nonnull;
004import javax.annotation.Nullable;
005import jsinterop.annotations.JsOverlay;
006import jsinterop.annotations.JsPackage;
007import jsinterop.annotations.JsType;
008import org.intellij.lang.annotations.MagicConstant;
009import react4j.dom.events.DragEventHandler;
010import react4j.dom.events.FocusEventHandler;

016/**
017 * Props for td elements. Refer to http://www.w3schools.com/tags/tag_td.asp
018 */
019@JsType( isNative = true, namespace = JsPackage.GLOBAL, name = "Object" )
020public class ThProps
021  extends HtmlGlobalFields<ThProps>
022{
023  @JsOverlay
024  @Nonnull
025  public final ThProps colSpan( int i )
026  {
027    setColSpan( i );
028    return self();
029  }
030
031  @JsOverlay
032  @Nonnull
033  public final ThProps headers( String headerId )
034  {
035    setHeaders( headerId );
036    return self();
037  }
038
039  @JsOverlay
040  @Nonnull
041  public final ThProps rowSpan( int i )
042  {
043    setRowSpan( i );
044    return self();
045  }
046
047  @JsOverlay
048  @Nonnull
049  public final ThProps scope( @MagicConstant( valuesFromClass = HeaderScope.class ) final String value )
050  {
051    setScope( value );
052    return self();
053  }
054
